reviews.comments: We had a fantastic stay at the house. Kartik and Richard were extremely responsive and gracious hosts. The property is stunning and the house is beautiful with uniquely curated decor.

Dear, Kartik,
We had an amazing time at your beautiful house; thank you for having us and we definitely look forward to coming back.
Nona and family.

I have been renting Airbnb's for some years now and this experience was by far the best!!! Not just because of Amazingly beautiful the hoke and surroundings are, but because Kartik is an EXCEPTIONAL host!!

Such a peaceful getaway for our family.  Was a little too cold for the pool but we enjoyed the hot tub and used the fireplace. It was so beautiful to wake up to gorgeous backyard and birdsong.  The host was very responsive.
